Summary: Six lights appeared in the sky and moved directly in front of the witness then disappeared
divs: Sighting DetailsWitness A was waiting in her PU Truck about dusk for her husband to finish plowing and when she looked up from reading a book, she saw six lights in the sky that appeared to be headlights. They moved from her right to directly in front of her and disappeared like a light switch was turned off. She saw no aircraft in the sky before or after the lights appeared and left.
trends: There have been 40 other sightings in Dublin
There were 2 other sightings in Dublin on or around January 10th 2008
